reekLit:tlg0003.tlg001.perseus-grc1:8:14\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Th.\">Th.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">8.14</biblScope></bibl>, etc.; in the Megarid, <abbr TEIform=\"abbr\">v.l. in</abbr> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:2:557\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.557</biblScope> </bibl>:—hence <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">Πολιχνῖται</orth>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">οἱ</gen>, inhabitants of a city in Crete, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:7:170\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hdt.\">Hdt.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">7.170</biblScope></bibl>.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}